extends ../main

block title
  | Account details changed - Username

block content
  +row
    p.
      Your username has been changed from #{oldUser.displayname} to #{user.displayname}.
  
  +row
    p.
      There is no need for verification, but if you didn't do this,
      your account was logged into by someone you shouldn't trust.
    
  +row
    p
      a(href="https://openusercss.org/account")
        | Click here if you want to reset your passphrase.
  
  +row(align="right")
    p Your new alias shall rise!

block reason
  | someone (hopefully you) changed your username
